<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <title>{% block title %}Sweeetch{% endblock %}</title>

        <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport">
        <meta content="" name="keywords">
        <meta content="" name="@">

        <link href="{{ asset('build/favicon.png') }}" rel="icon">
        <link href="{{ asset('build/apple-touch-icon.png') }}" rel="apple-touch-icon">

        {% block stylesheets %}
            <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/1596c4b58a.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>  
            <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:300,300i,400,400i,500,600,700,700i|Montserrat:300,400,500,600,700" rel="stylesheet">
            <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap-datepicker/1.9.0/css/bootstrap-datepicker.min.css">
            <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery-modal/0.9.1/jquery.modal.min.css" />
            <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.datatables.net/1.10.20/css/jquery.dataTables.min.css">
            {{ encore_entry_link_tags('student') }}
        {% endblock %}
    </head>
    <body>
        {# modal message #}
        <div id="help-1" class="modal">
            <div class="container" style="text-align:justify;">
                <h5>L'embauche se d√©roule en 5 √©tapes :</h5>
                <br>
                <ol>
                    <li>Cliquez sur <a class="btn btn-sm btn-success" style="color:white;">Chercher un emploi</a></li> et postulez aux offres de votre choix</li><br><br>
                    <li>D√®s qu'une entreprise vous recrute, l'√©tiquette <span class="badge badge-warning">√† valider</span> apparait dans la barre latt√©rale et les tableaux de candidatures. 
                    Vous pouvez accepter la mission en appuyant sur <button class="btn btn-success btn-sm"><i class="fas fa-user-check" title="Embaucher"></i>Accepter</button>
                    </li><br>
                    <li>Une fois la mission accept√©e, vous pouvez prendre contact avec l'entreprise pour signer un contrat d'alternance. Votre profil affiche alors : <span class="badge bg-info">Dossier en traitement</span></li><br>
                    <li>Une fois le contrat sign√©, votre profile affiche <span class="badge bg-success">En cours</span>. 
                    C'est le moment de chercher une √©cole en cliquant sur l'onglet <strong>Formations</strong> de la barre latt√©rale. 
                    </i></li><br>
                    <li>
                    Lorsque vous √™tes inscrits dans une √©cole, Sweeetch a accompli sa mission. C'est le moment de voler de vos propres ailes ! <a href="">#nostalgie</a> <br> <br>
                    La proc√©dure de recrutement est alors archiv√©e et consultable dans l'onglet <strong>Candidatures > Termin√©es</strong> de la barre latt√©rale.
                    </li><br>
                </ol>
                <p><strong>Nb :</strong> si vous souhaitez refuser d√©finitivement une mission, cliquez sur :   <button class="btn btn-danger btn-sm"><i class="fas fa-trash-alt"></i></button></p>
                <p><strong>Nb : Tous ces boutons apparaissent au fur et √† mesure de l'avanc√©e du recrutement. Si vous ne les trouvez pas tous en m√™me temps, c'est normal üòâ </strong></p>
                <p style="font-weight:900;">Bonne recherche !</p>
            </div> 
        </div>

        <div id="suppr-1" class="modal">
            <div class="container" style="text-align:justify;">
                <h5>Votre entreprise a supprim√© son compte</h5>
                <br>
                <p><strong>Pas de panique !</strong></p>
                <p>Si vous √™tes d√©j√† recrut√© sur Sweeetch vous gardez le droit de chercher une √©cole sur le site.</p>
                <p>Si vous n'√™tes pas encore recrut√© sur Sweeetch... vous serez oblig√©s de chercher un nouveau job ... <a href="">#d√©sol√©</a></p>
                <p style="font-weight:900;">Toutes nos excuses pour le d√©sagrement !</p>
            </div> 
        </div>
        {# warning form #}
        <div id="ex1" class="modal">
            {{ include('back/_warning_form.html.twig') }}
        </div>
        {# admin nav #}
        <div class="wrapper">
            <nav class="main-header navbar navbar-expand navbar-light">

                <ul class="navbar-nav">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" data-widget="pushmenu" href="#"><i class="fa fa-bars"></i></a>
                    </li>

                    <ul class="ul-ul">      
                        {% if is_granted('ROLE_ADMIN') %}
                        <li class="nav-item d-sm-inline-block" >
                            <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('admin') }}"> Admin </a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item d-none d-sm-inline-block">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('student_index') }}">Liste des √©tudiants</a>
                        </li>
                        {% endif %}
                        <li class="nav-item d-sm-inline-block">
                            <a href="/logout"  class="btn btn-outline-light">D√©connexion</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </ul>

            </nav>
        
            <aside class="main-sidebar sidebar-light-primary elevation-4">
                <a href="{{ path('homepage') }}" class="brand-link">
                    <img src="{{ asset('build/favicon.png') }}" alt="AdminLTE Logo" class="brand-image" style="opacity: .8">
                    <span class="brand-text font-weight-light"> Etudiant</span>
                </a>
                <div class="sidebar">
                    {# student infos #}
                    <div class="user-panel mt-3 pb-3 mb-3 d-flex">
                        {% if student.pictures.fileName is defined %}
                        <div class="image">
                            <img src="{{ uploaded_asset(student.pictures.fileName) }}" class="elevation-2" alt="User Image" style="                                   width: 200px;
                          height: 100px;max-width: 300px;max-height:120px;
                          object-fit: cover;">
                        </div>
                        {% else %}
                        <div>
                            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" style="width: 200px;
                            height: 100px;max-width: 300px;max-height:120px;
                            object-fit: cover;"/>                        
                        </div>
                        {% endif %}
                    </div>
                    <div class="user-panel mt-3 pb-3 mb-3 d-flex">
                        <div class="info">
                            <a href="{{ path('student_show', {'id' : student.id }) }}" class="d-block">{{ app.user.email }}</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <nav class="mt-2">
                        {# sidebar left #}
                        <ul class="nav nav-pills nav-sidebar flex-column" data-widget="treeview" role="menu" data-accordion="false">
                            <li class="nav-item has-treeview">
                                <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('student_show', {'id' : student.id }) }}">
                                    <i class="nav-icon fas fa-tachometer-alt"></i>
                                    <p>
                                        Tableau de Bord
                                    </p>
                                </a>
                            </li> 
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('student_edit', {'id' : student.id }) }}">
                                    <i class="nav-icon fa fa-user-circle"></i>
                                    <p>
                                        Infos du compte 
                                    </p>
                                </a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('profile_edit', {'id': student.profile.id, 'student_id':student.id }) }}">
                                    <i class="nav-icon fa fa-address-card"></i>
                                    <p>
                                        Profil Etudiant 
                                    </p>
                                </a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('student_apply', { id:student.id }) }}">
                                    <i class="nav-icon fa fa-bookmark"></i>
                                    <p>
                                        Candidatures  
                                        {# applies infos #}                                   
                                        {% if hired == true %}
                                        <span class="right badge badge-warning" title="mission √† confirmer">√† valider</span>
                                        {% elseif fresh > 0 %}
                                        <span class="badge badge-primary right" title="candidatures">{{ fresh }}</span> 
                                        {% endif %} 
                                    </p>
                                </a>
                                {% if is_granted('ROLE_SUPER_STUDENT') %}
                                    {% if app.request.get('_route') == 'student_apply' or app.request.get('_route') == 'offers_show_hired' or app.request.get('_route') == 'student_finished' %}

                                        <li class="nav nav-tree">
                                            <li class="nav-item">
                                                <a href="{{ path('student_apply', {id:student.id}) }}" class="nav-link">
                                                <i class="far fa-circle nav-icon"></i>
                                                <p>Toutes</p>
                                                </a>
                                            </li>
                                            <li class="nav-item">
                                                <a href="{{ path('student_finished', {id:student.id}) }}" class="nav-link">
                                                <i class="far fa-circle nav-icon"></i>
                                                <p>Termin√©es</p>
                                                {# finished applies infos #}
                                                {% if finished is defined %}
                                                    {% if finished | length > 0 %}
                                                <span class="right badge badge-warning">{{ finished | length }}</span>
                                                    {% endif %}
                                                {% endif %}
                                                </a>
                                            </li>
                                        </li>

                                    {% endif %} 
                                {% endif %}
                            </li>
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('school_student_index', { id:student.id }) }}">
                                    <i class="nav-icon fa fa-university"></i>
                                    <p>
                                        Formations 
                                        {# recruits infos #}
                                        {% if hiredRecruit == true %}
                                        <span class="right badge badge-warning" title="mission √† confirmer">√† valider</span>
                                        {% elseif freshRecruit > 0 %}
                                        <span class="badge badge-primary right" title="candidatures">{{ freshRecruit }}</span> 
                                        {% endif %}   
                                    </p>
                                </a>

                                {% if is_granted('ROLE_SUPER_STUDENT') %}
                                    {% if app.request.get('_route') == 'school_student_index' or app.request.get('_route') == 'show_student_hired' or app.request.get('_route') == 'school_student_finished'  %}

                                        <li class="nav nav-tree">
                                            <li class="nav-item">
                                                <a href="{{ path('school_student_index', { id:student.id }) }}" class="nav-link">
                                                <i class="far fa-circle nav-icon"></i>
                                                <p>Toutes</p>
                                                </a>
                                            </li>
                                            <li class="nav-item">
                                                <a href="{{ path('school_student_finished', {id:student.id}) }}" class="nav-link">
                                                <i class="far fa-circle nav-icon"></i>
                                                <p>Termin√©es</p>
                                                {# finished recruits infos #}
                                                {% if finished is defined %}
                                                    {% if finished | length > 0 %}
                                                <span class="right badge badge-warning">{{ finished | length }}</span>
                                                    {% endif %}
                                                {% endif %}
                                                </a>
                                            </li>
                                        </li>

                                    {% endif %} 
                                {% endif %}
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        <br><br>
                        <a class="btn btn-small btn-outline-success" id="tests" href="#test-1" rel="modal:open" style="display:block;margin:auto;">Pr√©sentation du Compte</a>
                    </nav>
                </div>
            </aside>

            {# content #}
            <div class="content-wrapper">
               <section class="content content-back">
                    {% block body %}{% endblock %}
                </section>
            </div>
            {# footer #}
            <footer class="main-footer">
                <strong>Sweeetch - Etudiant</strong>
            </footer>
        </div>

         {# test #}

         <div id="test-1" class="modal" style="max-width:700px;position:relative;">
            <div class="container" id="container-ajax">
                <div class="jumbotron">
                    <div class="modal-head">
                        <h3 style="color:black!important;text-align:center;">Bienvenue chez Sweeetch !</h3><br>
                        <p style="color:grey;text-align:justify;">Sweeetch vous permet de trouver rapidement un emploi et une formation en alternance. Dans cette courte pr√©sentation, nous vous montrons comment utiliser l'application.</p> <br>
                        <button class="btn btn-success" id="following-page" data-url="1" style="display:block;margin:auto;">Commencer <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
             {% if student.profile.presentation == NULL %}
             <div class="container" id="container-stop">
                <label for="input" id="label">
                    <input type="checkbox" name="input" id="input" data-url="{{ student.id }}">
                    Ne plus afficher ce message
                </label>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
        </div>

        {% block javascripts %}
        {{ encore_entry_script_tags('student') }}
        <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap-datepicker/1.9.0/js/bootstrap-datepicker.min.js"></script>
        <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery-modal/0.9.1/jquery.modal.min.js"></script>
        <script src="https://cdn.datatables.net/1.10.20/js/jquery.dataTables.min.js"></script>
        {% endblock %}
        
        {% if student.profile.presentation == NULL and app.request.get('_route') == 'student_show' %}
        <script>
            // presentation open popup
            $(document).ready(function() {
                $('#tests').click();
            });
        </script>
        {% endif %}

    </body>
</html>

